title: Eerie Publications (fills)
description:
I hope everyone has recovered from my earlier Eerie Publications upload (https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9215074/Eerie_Publications_(incomplete)), 'cause here's more of that crappy, haphazard, indifferent Goodness!

Beholds! I bring you 105 issues to plug into your EP collection. While most of these are mags that weren't in the first torrent, you'll find a few repeats in which I'm replacing partial scans with complete ones. And as an extra special cloacal bonus, I've included the recent book that celebrates these artistic monstrosities, "The Weird World of Eerie Publications", written by Mike Howlett, with a forward by Steve Bissette.

As always, mucho thanks to the people who garnered a paycheck for schlepping out these stories (aka, Creative Teams) and to the brave souls who risked eyesight and sanity to scan them for us. Please seed and keep this top-notch (chortle) product alive for future, inbred generations!
